cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.RO, cs.NE 

This paper involves the use of reinforcement learning (RL) to improve the performance of heuristic algorithms in solving combinatorial optimization problems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also involves optimization techniques, which could place it in cs.RO (Robotics and Control) and the use of neural networks, which could place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
